Welcome back to The Best & The Brightest. I=E2=80=99m Tara
Palmeri.

=C2=A0

Everyone in D.C. is pretty much frozen in fear=E2=80=94my phone has been bl=
owing up all week with officials from across the government telling me the =
same story: They=E2=80=99re not sure what to do, and the stress is making t=
hem less efficient at work. It all sounds the same. Am I going to get fired=
? Do I respond to this Elon Musk email? Will the DOGE boys come for my job =
next?
=E2=80=9CThere are 22-year-olds making calls like the gestapo, everyone is =
scared for their jobs, everyone is terrified,=E2=80=9D said one official. =
=E2=80=9CWe=E2=80=99re not supposed to say this is a gestapo, but it sure f=
eels like it.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0

=C2=A0

In tonight=E2=80=99s issue, news and notes on another Washington drama: the=
